transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Haan sir call drop ho gayi thi yahan thoda problem hai complaint kar kar ke thak gaya apne company mein sahi nahi kar pa rahe.
Customer: Koi baat nahi.
Executive: Haan haan to account ji.
Customer: Haan ab sir dekho do teen cheeze hai sir usko thoda aapko sahi karna hai ek to mujhe aap ye batao number kya tha unka madam ji ka matlab dusra number
Customer: Jinse jinse logout karwaya hai sir?
Executive: Ek to mujhe ye bata dijiye ye number kisi ke pass aapke pass hai 93 se start hai last mein 103 hai.
Customer: Ye mere pass hi hai sir ye to.
Executive: Bas theek hai yahi do number aapke hai jispe buyer ki call aayegi to koi teesra aur number abhi hai nahi theek hai.
Customer: Haan haan wo maine dalwai nahi hua sir isliye.
Executive: Achcha wo dalwaya hi nahi hua tha aapne bahut bahut achchi baat hai fir to theek hai ab jo hai aapka by jo buyers ki call aati hai na sir us pe thoda sa aapko dhyan dene ki zarurat hai wo kafi miss ho jati hai to koi naya employee rakhna agar to uska number add kara dena taki buyer ki call wo receive kar sake aap busy rahoge to kam se kam wo to receive karega theek hai rating and reviews aapka achcha hai kafi kahunga 4.6 out of five hai 22 reviews hai to sir recently koi customer India mart ke through ban paya hai ki nahi aapka.
Customer: Haan bana hai na sir.
Executive: Bahut achchi baat hai sir fir to achcha ab ye bataye all over India hum kam kar sakte hai ji kuch apna jo hai specific states mein hi pass ke states mein kar rahe hai abhi.
Customer: Nahi all over India hi karte hai ji.
Executive: Theek hai.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Ab jaise ek namkeen making machine ki aayi hai sir isme production capacity 200 kg per hour jhansi ki lead hai to ye okay okay hai ya isse capacity jyada chahiye hota hai aap jo banate ho production capacity jyada hai.
Customer: Okay okay hai sir sari lead aapki lagbhag okay hai actually ye is isko na wo nahi kar sakte sir matlab jo hai justify matlab ha differentiate nahi kar sakte kuch chezo ko.
Executive: Differentiate nahi kar sakte theek hai theek hai matlab samajh gaya lead wid lekar ke aur discussion karke samne buyer se to actual pata chalta hoga kai bar to ki kya chahiye kya akhir mein hai ki nahi sir.
Customer: Haan ji sir.
Executive: Nahi nahi theek hai overall to mujhe pata hai last time abhi ek hi hafta hua main aap se feedback bhi main liya tha isi wajah se fill karne ki wajah se to panch category d rank mein aa rahi thi to maine as it is add bhi kar diya tha aap usko thoda sa aap kam kar lena buyer ka reply reply to aap log badhiya kar hi rahe ho thoda sa bas ye hai ki jaise 270 agar inquiry aayi hai reply thoda kam hai sir half hai isko badhana aap jaise koi naya employee rakhna hire karna training time usse aap dilwa dena agar rakhna to hai na to bahut behtar rahega.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Catalog ka score pehle 80 tha abhi kam ho gaya kyuki maine panch product aise add kar diye jisme photo detail price nahi hai to score ghat gaya hai bas in panch pe sir kam kar lo koi problem nahi hai theek hai aur I hope sir aapka issue to maine solve kar diya to please sir mere liye feedback aayega usko sir zarur bhar dijiyega.
Customer: Main 100% kar dunga ji.
Executive: Mera naam zarur mention kar dena vikas sir.
Customer: Bilkul sir.
Executive: Theek hai ab to whatsapp pe bhi main add ho gaya hu to further koi query concern hai immediately aap message ya screenshot daloge na aap.
Customer: Ji ji ji.
Executive: To bas mera reply aa jayega aapke pass maine hello fir se kar diya aapko theek hai sir.
Customer: Theek hai sir theek hai ji thank you ji thank you very much.
Executive: Thank you sir have a nice day.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer was facing issues with company account.

- Buyers' calls are being missed.

- Catalog score decreased due to missing details.



Resolution:

- Executive provided guidance on account issues.

- Suggested adding new employee to receive calls.

- Advised on improving catalog details.



Next Steps: 

- Customer will fill out the feedback form.



Alert (If Any):

None
